{"questionId":"9076697","questionHtml":"<p>The radius of the bowl is 8.0 m and <em>θ</em> = 22°. Determine the speed of the ball.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{mg}}{{\\tan \\theta }}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>m</mi>\n      <mi>g</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>tan</mi>\n      <mo>⁡</mo>\n      <mi>θ</mi>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span> =&nbsp;<em>m</em><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{{v^2}}}{r}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>v</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mi>r</mi>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><em>r</em> = <em>R</em> cos&nbsp;<em>θ</em></p>\n<p><em>v</em> =&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\sqrt {\\frac{{gR{{\\cos }^2}\\theta }}{{\\sin \\theta }}} /\\sqrt {\\frac{{gR\\cos \\theta }}{{\\tan \\theta }}} /\\sqrt {\\frac{{9.81 \\times 8.0\\cos 22}}{{\\tan 22}}} \">\n  <msqrt>\n    <mfrac>\n      <mrow>\n        <mi>g</mi>\n        <mi>R</mi>\n        <mrow>\n          <msup>\n            <mrow>\n              <mi>cos</mi>\n            </mrow>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n        </mrow>\n        <mi>θ</mi>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mi>sin</mi>\n        <mo>⁡</mo>\n        <mi>θ</mi>\n      </mrow>\n    </mfrac>\n  </msqrt>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>/</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <msqrt>\n    <mfrac>\n      <mrow>\n        <mi>g</mi>\n        <mi>R</mi>\n        <mi>cos</mi>\n        <mo>⁡</mo>\n        <mi>θ</mi>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mi>tan</mi>\n        <mo>⁡</mo>\n        <mi>θ</mi>\n      </mrow>\n    </mfrac>\n  </msqrt>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>/</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <msqrt>\n    <mfrac>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>9.81</mn>\n        <mo>×</mo>\n        <mn>8.0</mn>\n        <mi>cos</mi>\n        <mo>⁡</mo>\n        <mn>22</mn>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mi>tan</mi>\n        <mo>⁡</mo>\n        <mn>22</mn>\n      </mrow>\n    </mfrac>\n  </msqrt>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><em>v</em> = 13.4/13&nbsp;<strong>«</strong><em>ms&nbsp;<sup>–</sup></em><em><sup>1</sup></em><strong>»</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Award </em><strong><em>[4] </em></strong><em>for a bald correct answer&nbsp;</em></p>\n<p><em>Award </em><strong><em>[3] </em></strong><em>for an answer of 13.9/14 </em><strong>«</strong><em>ms&nbsp;<sup>–</sup></em><em><sup>1</sup></em><strong>»</strong><em>. MP2 omitted</em></p>\n<p><strong><em>[4 marks]</em></strong></p>","meta":{"questionId":"9076697","referenceCode":"18M.2.HL.TZ2.b","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"The radius of the bowl is 8.0 m and θ = 22°. Determine the speed of the ball.","paper":"2","level":"HL","questionNumber":"b","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 4]","breadcrumbLabels":["Core","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics","2.2 – Forces","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}